Class MultisetTypeAdapter<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gson.TypeAdapter<Multiset<E>>
      • software.leonov.util.gson.MultisetTypeAdapter<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements contained in the Multiset

    public final class MultisetTypeAdapter<E>
extends TypeAdapter<Multiset<E>>
    A TypeAdapter which can serialize and deserialize of Multiset values to and from JSON.

      • MultisetTypeAdapter

        public MultisetTypeAdapter(Gson gson,
                           Type type,
                           Supplier<? extends Multiset<E>> supplier)
        Constructs a new MultisetTypeAdapter which can serialize and deserialize Multiset values.

        While this constructor can be invoked manually, it will most commonly be invoked by MultisetTypeAdapterFactory, which in turn will be registered with the provided Gson instance.

        Parameters:
        gson - a Gson instance which can handle the serialization and deserialization of the type of elements contained within the Multiset
        type - the Type of elements
        supplier - a Supplier which returns empty Multiset instances
